{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"2077","airdate":"1533664800","name_switch":"off","DJ":"ziona and Slaygon","showname":"Post-Datastorm evening with Jon Hare","blurb":"Hello Party people, Sofa sceners and SLAYPeeps! \n\nWe are back after a fantastic weekend at Datastorm, with a lot of great experiences and memories! Cool entries, nice conversations, new friendships and among them, we are proud to say that we had a great time talking with Jon Hare, the famous game designer of several titles like Sensible Soccer, Canon Fodder or Mega Lo Mania. We intend to continue this conversation on air now, so you can learn even more about the veteran game designer and musician! \n\nPrepare your requests and ears, SLAY with us for a pleasant post-party evening!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>ziona and Slaygon<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Post-Datastorm evening with Jon Hare","nice_airdate":"Tuesday 7th August, 2018<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2078","airdate":"1533837600","name_switch":"off","DJ":"KraxxUltima","showname":"Before Birthday Special Show","blurb":"Hyeah! And there you are. I'm also here, to temporarily disembark my \"unsinkable ship\" and cut the B-day cake with you guys doing a show the night before, So get your good requests in for any Commodore64 or Amiga tunes ya wanna hear. Bottoms Up and Have Fun! =)","nice_showname":"<strong><big>KraxxUltima<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Before Birthday Special Show","nice_airdate":"Thursday 9th August, 2018<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"}]}